desc: The model is a Christmas tree with pink lights, surrounded by presents. The presents are in different colours: green, red, and gold.
It is a coniferous tree with a single trunk and branches.

The model is a simple, white, low-poly 3D model of a bumpy, organic shape. It resembles a rock or a small asteroid.  It is not smooth but made up of triangular facets that make up a lumpy, irregular shape.
The model is a rough, rocky, grey-coloured asteroid or other space rock. It appears to be made of uneven, craggy surfaces.  It is irregular in shape.
The 3D model is a dark, textured, crater-like shape with cracks revealing a glowing, orange center. The cracks have a jagged and rough appearance.
The model is a plant in a white pot. It has a single stem with two small leaves at the top.
